Package: bsae
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Small Area Estimation
Version: 0.1.1
Author: Adam Howes
Maintainer: Adam Howes <ath19@ic.ac.uk>
Description: This package provides tools for small area estimation modelling
    in a Bayesian setting built on the inferential packages `rstan`,
    `R-INLA` and `TMB`. Models with a range of spatial random effects are
    implemented.
License: GPL (>= 2)
